MTN Zone i MTN PayAsYouGo price plan leyi ku pfumelelaka ku kuma ti discount to fika ka 95% loko u fonela ti nomboro ta MTN, yi nyika ti discount to fika 60% loko u fonela ti network tin'wana naleka ti sms. Discount yiya hi ndhawu leyi u vaka ka yona na awara ya kona. Loko u lava MTNZONE tshikelela *141*4*2# kumbe u fonela 141 option 4.